---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Services | Links AI"
  description="Links AI services: Strategy Sprint, Build + Launch, and ongoing support through Operate + Improve."
  pageClass="page-services"
>
  <section class="hero" slot="hero">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p>
      Our offering is structured as a simple ladder: define the opportunity,
      build the system, then improve it over time.
    </p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book an exploratory call</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What you can buy from us</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Strategy Sprint</h3>
        <p>A focused engagement to understand your operation, identify the highest-value AI opportunities, and map the right place to start.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Build + Launch</h3>
        <p>We design and implement the first working system inside your environment, then launch it with your team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Operate + Improve</h3>
        <p>We stay involved after launch to monitor performance, refine the workflow, and expand the system as it proves value.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>How to choose the right starting point</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Start with Strategy Sprint if...</h3>
        <p>You know AI matters, but you need clarity on where to start and what will create the most operational impact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Start with Build + Launch if...</h3>
        <p>You already know the workflow you want to improve and are ready to implement a real system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Add Operate + Improve if...</h3>
        <p>You want the system to keep getting better instead of becoming another static project that slowly drifts out of date.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-box">
    <h2>Not sure which service fits?</h2>
    <p>We can help you choose the right starting point based on your current operation and goals.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Request a call</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
